}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== '''Airgo 3000 Series''' ''USB Adapter 2x2'', aka '''''UB322gR'''''?
This device has two U.FL connectors.
A MAC label affixed to the device in the FCC photos reads '''000AF5BEF6C0''' (00:0A:F5 is '''Airgo''''s OUI). It has been assigned to this entry <small>for pretty much no reason</small>.
